user_query: I want to surprise my friends with the Thai lottery results for a specific date. Can you fetch the results for March 16, 2022? Additionally, I would like to know the latest draw date and a listing of all the draw dates. It would be great if you could generate a visually appealing report. Thank you very much!

TaskList.description: Fetch the Thai lottery results for the date March 16, 2022.
Fetch the latest draw date for the Thai lottery.
Fetch a listing of all the draw dates for the Thai lottery.
Generate a visually appealing report including results from step 1, latest draw date from step 2, and draw dates from step 3.
